quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  79,27,Kodi inu ndinu ovuta kulenga kapena thambo la mlengalenga limene Mulungu adalilenga
  79,28,Iye analikweza m’mwamba ndi kulikonza bwino
  79,29,Usiku wake amaukuta ndi m’dima ndipo masana ake amatulutsa kuwala
  79,30,Ndipo pambuyo pake adalikulitsa dziko
  79,31,Ndipo anatulutsa madzi ndi msipu
  79,32,Ndipo adazika mapiri molimbika
  79,33,Chakudya cha phindu kwa inu ndi kwa zoweta zanu
  79,34,Koma pamene mavuto akulu akudza
  79,35,Tsiku limene munthu adzayamba kuganiza ntchito zake zonse
  79,36,Ndipo Gahena idzabweretsedwa pafupi kuti aliyense aione
  79,37,Ndipo kwa iye ophwanya malamulo
  79,38,Ndipo anasankha moyo wapadziko lino
  79,39,Ndithudi malo ake okhala ndi ku Gahena
  79,40,Koma kwa iwo amene amaopa kukaima pamaso pa Ambuye wake ndi machimo ndipo anali kudziletsa kuchita chifuniro chopanda pake
  79,41,Ndithudi adzakhala ku Paradiso
  79,42,Amakufunsa za nthawi imene chigumula chidzabwere
  79,43,Iwe siudziwa zoti unene china chili chonse
  79,44,Ndi Ambuye wako yekha amene amadziwa tsiku
  79,45,Iwe ndiwe mchenjezi chabe kwa iwo amene ali kuliopa tsikuli
  79,46,"Patsiku limene iwo adzachiona chigumula, kudzakhala ngati kuti iwo sanakhale padziko lapansi nthawi yaitali koma usiku umodzi kapena usana wokha"